episodes.title: The Cult that Wanted to Take Over America | Children of Thunder
episodes.description:
The Helzer brothers, Taylor and Justin, were excommunicated from their religious community and developed a delusion of prophetic identity. They believed they were destined to herald a new era, and devised a sinister scheme involving criminal activities such as extortion, fraud, and murder to achieve their perceived divine mission.


Music by CO.AG
Video from Pexels.com
